    • Line

      public Line(String lineID, double lineR, double lineX, double lineY05, double lineChar, int busNo1, int busNo2, boolean lineIs, boolean hasTransformer, double turnsRatio, boolean tapAtLowerIndex)
      Parameters:
      lineID - Line ID
      lineR - Line's ohmic resistance [per units]
      lineX - Line's reactive impedance [per units]
      lineY05 - Line's half of shunt succeptance [per units]
      lineChar - Line's total charging [per units]
      busNo1 - Tap-bus (tap-changing) bus number
      busNo2 - Z-tap number
      lineIs - if line exists
      hasTransformer - if the Line has a transformer
      turnsRatio - turns Ratio
